 Vittorio Veneto.png|30px]] '''[[Vittorio Veneto Armored Brigade|Mechanized Brigade \"Vittorio Veneto\"]]''', in [[Villa Opicina]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Battle of Vittorio Veneto|Vittorio Veneto]]\", in Villa Opicina\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 02.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Piemonte Cavalleria\" (2nd)|2nd Mechanized Squadrons Group \"Piemonte Cavalleria\"]], in Villa Opicina, ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-2]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 06.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Lancieri di Aosta\" (6th)|6th Tank Squadrons Group \"Lancieri di Aosta\"]], in [[Cervignano del Friuli]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 09.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Lancieri di Firenze\" (9th)|9th Mechanized Squadrons Group \"Lancieri di Firenze\"]], in [[Sgonico]], (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 12.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Cavalleggeri di Saluzzo\" (12th)|12th Mechanized Squadrons Group \"Cavalleggeri di Saluzzo\"]], in [[Gorizia]], (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 001.png|25px]] 1st Motorized Infantry Battalion \"[[Justus of Trieste|San Giusto]]\", in [[Trieste]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 033.png|25px]] 33rd Infantry (Fortification) Battalion \"Ardenza\", in [[Fogliano Redipuglia]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria 008.png|25px]] 8th Self-propelled Field Artillery Group \"Pasubio\", in [[Trieste|Banne]], ([[M109 howitzer|M109 155mm]] [[Self-propelled artillery|self-propelled howitzers]])\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico vittorio veneto.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Vittorio Veneto\", in Cervignano del Friuli\n** Anti-tank Squadron \"Vittorio Veneto\", in Banne\n** Engineer Company \"Vittorio Veneto\", in Cervignano del Friuli\n\n==== Mechanized Brigade \"Gorizia\" ====\n* [[File:CoA mil ITA mec bde Gorizia.png|30px]] '''[[Gorizia Mechanized Brigade|Mechanized Brigade \"Gorizia\"]]''', i