irenze\"]], in [[Sgonico]], (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt cavalleria 12.png|25px]] [[Regiment \"Cavalleggeri di Saluzzo\" (12th)|12th Mechanized Squadrons Group \"Cavalleggeri di Saluzzo\"]], in [[Gorizia]], (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 001.png|25px]] 1st Motorized Infantry Battalion \"[[Justus of Trieste|San Giusto]]\", in [[Trieste]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 033.png|25px]] 33rd Infantry (Fortification) Battalion \"Ardenza\", in [[Fogliano Redipuglia]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria 008.png|25px]] 8th Self-propelled Field Artillery Group \"Pasubio\", in [[Trieste|Banne]], ([[M109 howitzer|M109 155mm]] [[Self-propelled artillery|self-propelled howitzers]])\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico vittorio veneto.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Vittorio Veneto\", in Cervignano del Friuli\n** Anti-tank Squadron \"Vittorio Veneto\", in Banne\n** Engineer Company \"Vittorio Veneto\", in Cervignano del Friuli\n\n==== Mechanized Brigade \"Gorizia\" ====\n* [[File:CoA mil ITA mec bde Gorizia.png|30px]] '''[[Gorizia Mechanized Brigade|Mechanized Brigade \"Gorizia\"]]''', in [[Gorizia]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"Gorizia\", in Gorizia\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt carri 002.png|25px]] 22nd Tank Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Piccinini\", in [[San Vito al Tagliamento]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 041.png|25px]] 41st Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[Modena]]\", in [[Villa Vicentina]], ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-2]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 053.png|25px]] 53rd Infantry (Fortification) Battalion \"[[Umbria]]\", in [[Pavia di Udine]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 063.png|25px]] 63rd Infantry (Fortification) Battalion \"[[Cagliari]]\", in [[San Lorenzo Isontino]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 082.png|25px]] 82nd Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[Turin|Torino]]\", in [[Cormons]], (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt paracadutisti 183.png|25px]] 183rd Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[184th Airborne Division Nembo|Nembo]]\", in [[Gradisca d'Isonzo]], (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA gr artiglieria 046.png|25px]] 46th Self-propelled Field Artillery Group \"[[Trento]]\", in Gradisca d'Isonzo, ([[M109 howitzer|M109 155mm]] [[Self-propelled artillery|self-propelled howitzers]])\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg logistico gorizia.png|25px]] Logistic Battalion \"Gorizia\", in Gradisca d'Isonzo\n** Anti-tank Company \"Gorizia\", in Gorizia\n** Engineer Company \"Gorizia\", in Cormons\n\n==== Mechanized Brigade \"Mantova\" ====\n* [[File:CoA mil ITA mec bde Mantova.png|30px]] '''[[Mantova Mechanized Brigade|Mechanized Brigade \"Mantova\"]]''', in [[Udine]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Mantova]]\", in [[Udine]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt carri 063.png|25px]] 63rd Tank Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Fioritto\", in [[Cordenons]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 052.png|25px]] 52nd Infantry (Fortification) Battalion \"[[Alps|Alpi]]\", in [[Attimis]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 059.png|25px]] 59th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[Calabria]]\", in [[Cividale del Friuli]], ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-2]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 076.png|25px]] 76th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[Naples|Napoli]]\", in Cividale del Friuli, (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 114.png|25px]] 114th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"[[Moriago della Battaglia|Moriago]]\", in [[Tricesimo]], (VCC-2 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 120.png|25px]] 120th Infantry (Fortification) Battalion \"Fornovo\", in [[Premariacco|Ipplis]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria 028.png|25px]] 28th Self-propelled Field Artiller