ed howitzers)\n** 10th Artillery Specialists Battery, in Foggia\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt genio 21.png|25px]] 21st Engineer Battalion \"[[Timavo]]\", in [[Caserta]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt trasmissioni 45.png|25px]] 45th Signal Battalion \"[[Monte Vulture|Vulture]]\", in Naples\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt logistico pinerolo.png|25px]] 10th Mixed Transport Battalion \"[[Appian Way|Appia]]\", in Naples\n** Logistic Battalion \"Persano\" , in Persano (activated 30 April 1989 to prepare for the arrival of the \"Garibaldi\" Brigade)\n** 20th Light Airplanes and Helicopters Squadrons Group \"[[Andromeda (constellation)|Andromeda]]\", at [[Salerno Costa d'Amalfi Airport|Salerno-Pontecagnano Air Base]], ([[SIAI-Marchetti SM.1019|SM-1019]] planes and [[Bell 206|AB-206]] helicopters)\n** 10th Supply Unit, in Bari\n** 10th Provisions Supply Company, in Naples\n** 10th Medical Company, in Bari\n** Military Hospital Type A, in Bari\n** Military Hospital Type A, in Caserta\n** Military Hospital Type B, in Naples\n** Military Hospital Type B, in Catanzaro\n\n==== Mechanized Brigade \"Pinerolo\" ====\n* [[File:CoA of the Pinerolo Brigade.svg|30px]] '''[[Pinerolo Mechanized Brigade|Mechanized Brigade \"Pinerolo\"]]''', in [[Bari]]\n** Command and Signal Unit \"[[Pinerolo]]\", in [[Bari]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg carri 060.png|25px]] 60th Tank Battalion \"[[Gold Medal of Military Valor|M.O.]] Locatelli\", in [[Altamura]], ([[Leopard 1|Leopard 1A2]] [[main battle tank]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 009.png|25px]] 9th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"Bari\", in [[Trani]], ([[M113 armored personnel carrier|VCC-1]] [[armored personnel carrier]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg fanteria 013.png|25px]] 13th Mechanized Infantry Battalion \"Valbella\", in Avellino, (VCC-1 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt bersaglieri 18.png|25px]] 67th Bersaglieri Battalion \"Fagar\u00e8\", in [[Serre, Campania|Persano]], (VCC-1 armored personnel carriers)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA