lieria c a 005.png|25px]] 5th Anti-aircraft Missile Artillery Regiment \"[[Pescara]]\", in [[Mestre]]\n*** Command Battery, Mestre\n*** 1st Anti-aircraft Missile Artillery Group, in [[San Don\u00e0 di Piave]], (MIM-23 Hawk surface-to-air missiles)\n*** 2nd Anti-aircraft Missile Artillery Group, in [[Rovigo]], (MIM-23 Hawk surface-to-air missiles)\n*** 25th Signal Company, in Mestre\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria c a 121.png|25px]] 121st Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Regiment \"[[Ravenna]]\", in Bologna\n*** 1st Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Group, in Bologna\n*** 2nd Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Group, in Mestre\n*** 3rd Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Group, in [[Rimini]]\n*** 4th Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Group, in [[Ferrara]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt artiglieria c a 017.png|25px]] 17th Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Group \"Sforzesca\", at [[Villafranca Air Base]]\n*** Command Battery, at Villafranca Air Base\n*** 1st Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Battery, at Villafranca Air Base\n*** 2nd Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Battery, at [[Ghedi Air Base]]\n*** 3rd Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Battery, at [[Treviso-Istrana Air Base|Istrana Air Base]]\n*** 4th Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Battery, at [[Federico Fellini International Airport|Rimini Air Base]]\n*** 5th Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Battery, at [[Cervia Air Force Base|Cervia Air Base]]\n** 21st Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Group \"[[Eurasian sparrowhawk|Sparviero]]\" (Reserve), in [[Villafranca]]\n** 22nd Light Anti-aircraft Artillery Group \"[[Common kingfisher|Alcione]]\" (Reserve), in [[Bologna]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt fanteria 235.png|25px]] 235th Infantry (Recruits Training) Battalion \"Piceno\", in [[Ascoli Piceno]]\n** Anti-aircraft Missiles Supply and Repairs Unit, in [[Montichiari]]\n** Anti-aircraft Artillery Materiel Supply and Repairs Unit, in [[Bologna]]\n\n=== Units directly reporting to the Army General Staff ===\n* '''Army General Staff''', in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt aves 1.png|25px]] 1st Army Aviation Regiment \"[[Antares]]\", in [[Viterbo]]\n*** 11th Transport Helicopter Squadrons Group \"[[Hercules (constellation)|Ercole]]\", in Viterbo, ([[Boeing CH-47 Chinook|CH-47C Chinook]] heavy-lift helicopters)\n*** 12th Helicopter (Reserve) Squadrons Group \"[[Grus (constellation)|Gru]]\", in Viterbo, providing pilots to other units\n*** 39th Helicopter Squadrons Group \"[[Dragon|Drago]]\", in [[Alghero-Fertilia Airport|Alghero-Fertilia]], detached to the military intelligence agency [[SISMI]]\n*** 51st Medium Helicopter Squadrons Group \"[[Leo (constellation)|Leone]]\", in Viterbo, ([[Bell 412|AB-412]] [[utility helicopter]]s)\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg NBC 01.png|25px]] 1st [[CBRN defense|CBRN-defense]] Battalion \"[[Etruria]]\", in [[Rieti]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg ricel 08.png|25px]] 8th [[ELINT]] Battalion \"[[Tonale Pass|Tonale]]\", in [[Anzio]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA btg guelt 09.png|25px]] 9th [[Electronic Warfare]] Battalion \"[[Timmelsjoch|Rombo]]\", in Anzio\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt trasmissioni 03.png|25px]] 10th Signal Battalion \"[[Lanciano]]\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt trasmissioni 11.png|25px]] 11th Signal Battalion \"[[Leonessa]]\", in Civitavecchia\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA autogr manovra 10.png|25px]] 10th Joint Transport Battalion \"[[Via Salaria|Salaria]]\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA autogr manovra 11.png|25px]] 11th Transport Battalion \"[[Via Flaminia|Flaminia]]\", in Rome\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt sost aves 1.png|25px]] 1st Army Aviation Maintenance Battalion \"[[Hydra (constellation)|Idra]]\", in [[Bracciano]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt sost aves 2.png|25px]] 2nd Army Aviation Maintenance Battalion \"[[Orion (constellation)|Orione]]\", in [[Bologna]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt sost aves 3.png|25px]] 3rd Army Aviation Maintenance Battalion \"[[Aquila (constellation)|Aquila]]\", in [[Orio al Serio]]\n** [[File:CoA mil ITA rgt sost aves 4.png|25px]] 4th Army Aviation Maintenance Battalion \"[[